snippet.title: Temtem: Swarm - Official Gameplay Trailer | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description: Check out gameplay and the colorful world and creatures of Temtem: Swarm in this trailer for the upcoming bullet-heaven game. Temtem: Swarm combines the strategic elements of Temtem combat with the frenetic gameplay of classic survivor games. Temtem: Swarm will be available on PC. Prepare to team up with friends in online co-op for up to three players and face relentless swarms of enemies, unlock powerful abilities and upgrades, find and collect Tems to evolve and become stronger, and battle massive bosses.
